1. On je na *početku* imao malo novca, ali je uspeo da postane bogat. (He had a little money at the beginning, but he managed to become rich.)

2. *Početku* se nije nadao da će postići tako mnogo. (He didn't hope at the beginning to achieve so much.)

3. Ona je na *početku* bio skeptična prema novom projektu. (She was skeptical at the beginning about the new project.)

4. U *početku* je bilo teško, ali sada je sve lakše. (It was hard at the beginning, but now everything is easier.)

5. On je oštro reagovao na *početku*. (He reacted harshly at the beginning.)